entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the first Imperial Officer from the Rebel Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Go to the Rebel Detainment Facility and rescue the first Imperial Officer being held prisoner.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go back to the Detainment Facility at the Rebel Hideout on Corellia.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go back to the Detainment Facility
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat Jorel Sherrol in combat and take his Rebel Trooper Armor.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Get the disguise from Jorel Sherrol
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Destroy the Blastromech near the Detainment Center entrance.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat Rebel Commandos guarding to the Rebel Detention Center.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: I've sliced Sherrol's datapad and now we have a basic idea where all 6 of the prisoners are being held.  Great work.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Search the holding cells located at the North holding wing of the facility. This is somewhere near the front of the Detainment Facility.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Give the officer the disguise you have.
